===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|abreggen||curtail, lessen}}, {{m|enm|abregge}}, {{m|enm|abrigge}},<ref> {{R:RHCD|page=5}}</ref> from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|abregier|}} {{m|fro|abreger|}}, from {{etyl|LL.|en}} {{m|la|abbrevio||make brief}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|ad|}} + {{m|la|brēvio||shorten}}.<ref>{{R:MW3 1976|page=6}}</ref>

